@META
dir: /
updated: 2026-04-15
files: 2
stack: Remotion 4, React 19, TypeScript 5.4, Phosphor Icons, Montserrat + IBM Plex Mono

@EXPORTS
(no code exports at root — monorepo wrapper)

@VARS_CONSTANTS
BRAND: Praut s.r.o. — Martin Švanda AI Channel
VIDEO_DIMS: 1920×1080 (long) | 1080×1920 (short) | 1080×1080 (square) @ 30fps
PROD_EPISODE: EP01 = 38160 frames (~21 min, 93 scenes)

@PROCESSES
video-production: tokens.ts → components (152) → templates (10) → compositions → Remotion render → mp4
skill-install: scripts/install-skill.sh → symlink skills/remotion → ~/.claude/skills/remotion
phosphor-extraction: scripts/extract-phosphor-glyphs.mjs → phosphor-icons/Fonts/*/style.css → phosphor-glyphs.json

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: skillsPraut/ (single workspace)
external: none at root

@STANDARDS
- Single source of truth: skillsPraut/src/styles/tokens.ts
- Colors: navy 60% | blue accent 30% | purple CTA 10%
- Fonts: Montserrat primary + IBM Plex Mono mono | fontWeight ≥ 500 on dark mode
- Never hardcode hex outside tokens.ts
- glow.* instead of rgba boxShadow
- Springs & timing.* presets only — no custom animation curves
- Czech diacritics via latin-ext subset
- Layouts: singleFocus | splitScreen only
- safeZone: 64px padding all sides
- Branch: main | gitignore: node_modules, out/, renders/*.mp4

@WARNINGS
- skillsPraut/renders/ untracked (large mp4 outputs & PNG frames)
- skillsPraut/out/ untracked (per-frame render PNGs)
- public/fonts/phosphor/ contains 6 binary font variants (thin..duotone)
- phosphor-icons/ referenced by extract script but not in working tree (removed)
